# Complete Project Folder Structure
## Predictive Cognitive State Modeling — Adaptive Game Difficulty Regulation

> Scalable, modular, production-ready layout.
> Each file entry documents: **purpose**, **contents**, and **dependencies**.

---

## Full Directory Tree

```
NLP-RP/
│
├── app/                            ← FastAPI backend application
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── main.py                     ← App factory, CORS, route registration
│   ├── api/                        ← HTTP interface layer
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   ├── routes.py               ← All endpoint definitions
│   │   └── schemas.py              ← Pydantic request/response models
│   ├── core/                       ← Business logic (CII pipeline)
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   ├── config.py               ← System-wide configuration
│   │   ├── telemetry.py            ← D(t): performance deviation
│   │   ├── nlp.py                  ← P(t), I(t), G(t): NLP features
│   │   ├── emotional_dynamics.py   ← E(t), M(t), A(t), CII(t)
│   │   ├── predictor.py            ← State prediction (blended)
│   │   └── controller.py          ← Adaptive difficulty controller
│   └── models/                     ← ML model definitions
